snippet.title: Luigi and the Violet Stars (Savestateless)
snippet.description:
Hello! This was my live playthrough of Luigi and the Violet Stars by usernamesarespiders.

Review: Very good hack. The music is great, levels are good. The new comet stars are fun. The koopa the quick in blossoming fields crashes unless you don't turn off "Advanced Block Lining" in Recompiler in settings.

Streamed Live at: https://www.twitch.tv/ozsef
My Romhacking.com Page: https://romhacking.com/user/Ozsef
